{"lineNumber":196199,"originalJapaneseLine":"「山の上なのに妙に湿度が高くて、","translatedEnglishLine":"'Even though it's on a mountain, the humidity is strangely high,"},{"lineNumber":196200,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それでいて気温が高くて風が冷たいのは","translatedEnglishLine":"and yet the temperature is high but the wind is cold,"},

{"lineNumber":196201,"originalJapaneseLine":"　その辺が影響してるとか」","translatedEnglishLine":"I heard that's because of that area’s influence.'"},

{"lineNumber":196202,"originalJapaneseLine":"「へー、詳しいね、長田君」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Wow, you know a lot, Nagata-kun.'"},

{"lineNumber":196203,"originalJapaneseLine":"「まあまあ、俺らはもう既に登ったことがあるから？","translatedEnglishLine":"'Well, well, it's because we've already climbed it before, so?"},

{"lineNumber":196204,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんかよく分からないことがあったら","translatedEnglishLine":"'If there's anything you don’t understand,"},

{"lineNumber":196205,"originalJapaneseLine":"　聞いてくれていいから！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'feel free to ask us!'"},

{"lineNumber":196206,"originalJapaneseLine":"「調子乗ってんじゃねーぞ、陶器」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Don't get cocky, pottery.'"},

{"lineNumber":196207,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あんっ、踏むなよぉ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Ah, don't step on me...'"},

{"lineNumber":196208,"originalJapaneseLine":"「まったく、やめなさい……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Honestly, stop it...'"},

{"lineNumber":196209,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"'........' "},

{"lineNumber":196210,"originalJapaneseLine":"「？　どうかしたの？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hmm? What's wrong?'"},

{"lineNumber":196211,"originalJapaneseLine":"レリコフが大きな岩を、ジッと強く睨んでいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Lerikov was staring intensely at a large rock."},

{"lineNumber":196212,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なにかいる」","translatedEnglishLine":"'There's something there.'"},

{"lineNumber":196213,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……え？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'...Huh?'"},

{"lineNumber":196214,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなた達の中でも戦士タイプの一部が、","translatedEnglishLine":"Among you, some of the warrior types were,"},

{"lineNumber":196215,"originalJapaneseLine":"岩陰をジッと睨みつけていた。","translatedEnglishLine":"also staring intently at the shadow behind the rock."},

{"lineNumber":196216,"originalJapaneseLine":"「――みんな、警戒を。","translatedEnglishLine":"'Everyone, be on guard."},

{"lineNumber":196217,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そこに敵がいる」","translatedEnglishLine":"'There is an enemy there.' "},

{"lineNumber":196218,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えっ、えっ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'W-What!?' "},

{"lineNumber":196219,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ハッ、敵意バリバリだな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hah, there's clearly hostile intent...'"},

{"lineNumber":196220,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そこにいるのは何者だ！　姿を見せろ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Whoever’s there! Show yourself!'"},

{"lineNumber":196221,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふふ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Heh heh...'"},

{"lineNumber":196222,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くくく……相変わらず……","translatedEnglishLine":"'Kukuku... as always...'"},

{"lineNumber":196223,"originalJapaneseLine":"　嫌味なくらい優秀な子供達だねぇ」","translatedEnglishLine":"'You kids are annoyingly talented, aren't you?'"},

{"lineNumber":196224,"originalJapaneseLine":"「タイガー将軍！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'General Tiger!?'"},

{"lineNumber":196225,"originalJapaneseLine":"「アア？　なんでここに……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Huh? Why are you here...'"},

{"lineNumber":196226,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふふ、くく……おじさんの任務は一つ……","translatedEnglishLine":"'Heh heh, kuku... my mission is just one thing...'"},

{"lineNumber":196227,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王の子達の抹殺……","translatedEnglishLine":"'The extermination of the Demon King's children...'"},

{"lineNumber":196228,"originalJapaneseLine":"　君達のいる所に現れるのは当然だろう？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'So it's only natural I appear where you are, right?'"},

{"lineNumber":196229,"originalJapaneseLine":"タイガー将軍の瞳は赤く血走り、","translatedEnglishLine":"General Tiger’s eyes were bloodshot red,"},

{"lineNumber":196230,"originalJapaneseLine":"今までとは違う危険な気配を発していた。","translatedEnglishLine":"exuding a dangerous aura unlike before."},

{"lineNumber":196231,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ハッ、逆恨みでトチ狂ったか。","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hah, have you gone crazy out of spite?"},

{"lineNumber":196232,"originalJapaneseLine":"　三万の兵連れて負けたのに一人で何する気だ」","translatedEnglishLine":"You lost with thirty thousand soldiers, so what are you planning to do alone?'"},

{"lineNumber":196233,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いやぁ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Well...'"},

{"lineNumber":196234,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おじさんも色々と考えに考えたけど……","translatedEnglishLine":"'I’ve thought and thought about it too...'"},

{"lineNumber":196235,"originalJapaneseLine":"　やはり、これしかないか、って……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'I came to the conclusion that this is the only way...'"},

{"lineNumber":196236,"originalJapaneseLine":"「もう正直、ね……","translatedEnglishLine":"'To be honest now...'"},

{"lineNumber":196237,"originalJapaneseLine":"　君達を殺せるか否かはどうでも良くてね……","translatedEnglishLine":"'Whether I can kill you or not doesn’t really matter...'"},

{"lineNumber":196238,"originalJapaneseLine":"「大事なのは、","translatedEnglishLine":"'What matters is...'"},

{"lineNumber":196239,"originalJapaneseLine":"　僕があの子達の為に何が出来るか……","translatedEnglishLine":"'what I can do for those kids...'"},

{"lineNumber":196240,"originalJapaneseLine":"　だ、だから……だから……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'So, that’s why... that’s why...'"},

{"lineNumber":196241,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"'........' "},

{"lineNumber":196242,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あんた、なにを言って……」","translatedEnglishLine":"'What are you saying...'"},

{"lineNumber":196243,"originalJapaneseLine":"「地獄まで付き合ってもらうよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"'You'll come with me to hell.' "},

{"lineNumber":196244,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うあっ、ぐうっ……！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Ugh, guhh...!'"},

{"lineNumber":196245,"originalJapaneseLine":"タイガー将軍が己の首に注射器の針を突き立てた。","translatedEnglishLine":"General Tiger plunged the needle of a syringe into his own neck."},

{"lineNumber":196246,"originalJapaneseLine":"「わあ、なになになに！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Wah, what, what, what!?' "},

{"lineNumber":196247,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はっ、か、ぐっ！　ぐううううう！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Hah, guh, guuuu!?' "},

{"lineNumber":196248,"originalJapaneseLine":"タイガー将軍がその場に崩れ落ちて、","translatedEnglishLine":"General Tiger collapsed on the spot,"},

{"lineNumber":196249,"originalJapaneseLine":"もがき苦しみだす。","translatedEnglishLine":"writhing in pain."},

{"lineNumber":196250,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああぁああぁあああああ！！！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"'Aaaaaaahhhhhhh!!!'"},

{"lineNumber":196251,"originalJapaneseLine":"この世の物とは思えぬ悲鳴。","translatedEnglishLine":"A scream that did not seem of this world."}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああもう、やめなさい」
結局、その話はここでうやむやのまま終わり――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end, that conversation ended here in ambiguity—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達はまた黙々と翔竜山を登ることにした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You all silently decided to continue climbing Mount Shoryu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ、はあ……なんだか、息苦しい、ね……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Hah, hah... somehow, it's suffocating, isn't it...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おー、話によると魔王の近くは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Oh, according to what I've heard, near the Demon King—'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自然と人の住みにくい土地になるから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: —it naturally becomes land that's hard for people to live in,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 翔竜山もどんどんそうなってるらしいよ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Mount Shoryu is gradually becoming like that too.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「山の上なのに妙に湿度が高くて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Even though it's on a mountain, the humidity is strangely high,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それでいて気温が高くて風が冷たいのは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and yet the temperature is high but the wind is cold,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その辺が影響してるとか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I heard that's because of that area’s influence.'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「へー、詳しいね、長田君」
「まあまあ、俺らはもう既に登ったことがあるから？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Well, well, it's because we've already climbed it before, so?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんかよく分からないことがあったら
聞いてくれていいから！」
「調子乗ってんじゃねーぞ、陶器」
「あんっ、踏むなよぉ……」
「まったく、やめなさい……」
「？　どうかしたの？」
レリコフが大きな岩を、ジッと強く睨んでいた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lerikov was staring intensely at a large rock.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なにかいる」
あなた達の中でも戦士タイプの一部が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Among you, some of the warrior types were,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 岩陰をジッと睨みつけていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: also staring intently at the shadow behind the rock.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「――みんな、警戒を。
そこに敵がいる」
「えっ、えっ！？」
「ハッ、敵意バリバリだな……」
「そこにいるのは何者だ！　姿を見せろ！」
「くくく……相変わらず……
嫌味なくらい優秀な子供達だねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'You kids are annoyingly talented, aren't you?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「タイガー将軍！？」
「アア？　なんでここに……」
「ふふ、くく……おじさんの任務は一つ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Heh heh, kuku... my mission is just one thing...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の子達の抹殺……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'The extermination of the Demon King's children...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達のいる所に現れるのは当然だろう？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'So it's only natural I appear where you are, right?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: タイガー将軍の瞳は赤く血走り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger’s eyes were bloodshot red,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今までとは違う危険な気配を発していた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: exuding a dangerous aura unlike before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ハッ、逆恨みでトチ狂ったか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Hah, have you gone crazy out of spite?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 三万の兵連れて負けたのに一人で何する気だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You lost with thirty thousand soldiers, so what are you planning to do alone?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いやぁ……」
「おじさんも色々と考えに考えたけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'I’ve thought and thought about it too...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やはり、これしかないか、って……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'I came to the conclusion that this is the only way...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もう正直、ね……
君達を殺せるか否かはどうでも良くてね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Whether I can kill you or not doesn’t really matter...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「大事なのは、
僕があの子達の為に何が出来るか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'what I can do for those kids...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だ、だから……だから……」
「あんた、なにを言って……」
「地獄まで付き合ってもらうよ」
「うあっ、ぐうっ……！」
タイガー将軍が己の首に注射器の針を突き立てた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger plunged the needle of a syringe into his own neck.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わあ、なになになに！？」
「はっ、か、ぐっ！　ぐううううう！？」
タイガー将軍がその場に崩れ落ちて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger collapsed on the spot,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もがき苦しみだす。
「ああぁああぁあああああ！！！！」
この世の物とは思えぬ悲鳴。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A scream that did not seem of this world.

translationLines.description: Array of objects, each representing a line from the input

originalJapaneseLine.description: The original line in Japanese exactly as it was in the input

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English

「そこにいるのは何者だ！　姿を見せろ！」
「くくく……相変わらず……
嫌味なくらい優秀な子供達だねぇ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'You kids are annoyingly talented, aren't you?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「タイガー将軍！？」
「アア？　なんでここに……」
「ふふ、くく……おじさんの任務は一つ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Heh heh, kuku... my mission is just one thing...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の子達の抹殺……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'The extermination of the Demon King's children...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 君達のいる所に現れるのは当然だろう？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'So it's only natural I appear where you are, right?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: タイガー将軍の瞳は赤く血走り、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger’s eyes were bloodshot red,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今までとは違う危険な気配を発していた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: exuding a dangerous aura unlike before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ハッ、逆恨みでトチ狂ったか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Hah, have you gone crazy out of spite?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 三万の兵連れて負けたのに一人で何する気だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You lost with thirty thousand soldiers, so what are you planning to do alone?'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いやぁ……」
「おじさんも色々と考えに考えたけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'I’ve thought and thought about it too...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やはり、これしかないか、って……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'I came to the conclusion that this is the only way...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もう正直、ね……
君達を殺せるか否かはどうでも良くてね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'Whether I can kill you or not doesn’t really matter...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「大事なのは、
僕があの子達の為に何が出来るか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: 'what I can do for those kids...'

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だ、だから……だから……」
「あんた、なにを言って……」
「地獄まで付き合ってもらうよ」
「うあっ、ぐうっ……！」
タイガー将軍が己の首に注射器の針を突き立てた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger plunged the needle of a syringe into his own neck.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わあ、なになになに！？」
「はっ、か、ぐっ！　ぐううううう！？」
タイガー将軍がその場に崩れ落ちて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: General Tiger collapsed on the spot,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もがき苦しみだす。
「ああぁああぁあああああ！！！！」
この世の物とは思えぬ悲鳴。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A scream that did not seem of this world.
